title: Kyle Shanahanigans
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth recap the 49ers win against the Rams. Is the season over for the Rams? Do the 49ers have the best defense in football? Plus Mina and Domonique and give their Winners & Woofs for Week 4, and both of them are extremely high on Pete Carroll & Geno Smith this week.
